Name: Tychus Findlay
Description: One of the Guns. Adept at all aspects of combat. Can use Shredder Grenade.**Can attack ground and air units**

Root.Tooltip: Orders selected units to move to the target area or follow the target unit. Moving units will not engage enemies.
Root.Name: Move

Root.Tooltip: Orders selected units to cancel all orders and stop moving.
Root.Name: Stop

Root.Tooltip: Orders selected units to stay where they are and attack enemies that are within range. Units will neither chase down enemies nor move to engage.
Root.Name: Hold Position

Root.Tooltip: Orders selected units to patrol between their current position and the target area. Units will attack enemies and move to engage nearby enemies.
Root.Name: Patrol

Root.Tooltip: Calls down a Nuclear Strike at a target location. Nukes take 3 seconds to land, but they deal up to 1000 damage in a large area.
Root.Name: Big Red Button

Root.Tooltip: Deals 75 damage to enemy units in the target area.
Root.Name: Shredder Grenade

Root.Tooltip: Deals 75 damage to enemy units in the target area.
Root.Name: Shredder Grenade

Root.Tooltip: Stuns all enemies and deals 1000 damage over 5 seconds in a large area.
Root.Name: Barrage

Root.Tooltip: You haven't picked up the corresponding blueprints.
Root.Name: SureShot Networked Helmet

Root.Tooltip: Increases Tychus' weapon damage by 20% for each Outlaw in his immediate vicinity.
Root.Name: SureShot Networked Helmet

Root.Tooltip: Orders selected units to move to the target point, fighting nearby enemies along the way. Targeting a unit with the Attack command orders that it be attacked until it is destroyed.
Root.Name: Attack

Root.Tooltip: Increases the damage of Tychus' Shredder Grenade by 50.
Root.Name: Vanadium Shell

Root.Tooltip: Tychus' attacks decrease the armor of their targets by 5 for 2 seconds.
Root.Name: Kel-Morian Ripper Rounds

Root.Tooltip: Allows Shredder Grenade to pull affected units to the center of its area of effect, stunning them for 2 seconds.
Root.Name: KD9a Implosion Core
